quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  13,5,WE ‘IN TA’XHEB FE’AXHEBUN KAWLUHUM ‘E’IDHA KUNNA TURABÆN ‘E’INNA LEFI HALKIN XHEDIDIN ‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE KEFERU BIREBBIHIM WE ‘ULA’IKEL-’EGLALU FI ‘A’NAKIHIM WE ‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABU EN-NARI HUM FIHA HALIDUNE
  13,6,WE JESTA’XHILUNEKE BIS-SEJJI’ETI KABLEL-HESENETI WE KAD HALET MIN KABLIHIMUL-METHULATU WE ‘INNE REBBEKE LEDHU MEGFIRETIN LILNNASI ‘ALA DHULMIHIM WE ‘INNE REBBEKE LESHEDIDUL-’IKABI
  13,7,WE JEKULUL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEWLA ‘UNZILE ‘ALEJHI ‘AJETUN MIN RABBIHI ‘INNEMA ‘ENTE MUNDHIRUN WE LIKULLI KAWMIN HADIN
  13,8,ELLAHU JA’LEMU MA TEHMILU KULLU ‘UNTHA WE MA TEGIDUL-’ERHAMU WE MA TEZDADU WE KULLU SHEJ’IN ‘INDEHU BIMIKDARIN
  13,9,‘ALIMUL-GAJBI WE ESH-SHEHADETIL-KEBIRUL-MUTA’ALI
  13,10,SEWA’UN MINKUM MEN ‘ESERREL-KAWLE WE MEN XHEHERE BIHI WE MEN HUWE MUSTEHFIN BIL-LEJLI WE SARIBUN BIN-NEHARI
  13,11,LEHU MU’AKKIBATUN MIN BEJNI JEDEJHI WE MIN HALFIHI JEHFEDHUNEHU MIN ‘EMRI ELLAHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JUGAJJIRU MA BIKAWMIN HETTA JUGAJJIRU MA BI’ENFUSIHIM WE ‘IDHA ‘ERADEL-LAHU BIKAWMIN SU’ÆN FELA MEREDDE LEHU WE MA LEHUM MIN DUNIHI MIN WE E
  13,12,HUWEL-LEDHI JURIKUMUL-BERKA HAWFÆN WE TEMA’ÆN WE JUNSHI’U ES-SEHABE ETH-THIKALE
  13,13,WE JUSEBBIHU ER-RA’DU BIHEMDIHI WEL-MELA’IKETU MIN HIFETIHI WE JURSILU ES-SEWA’IKA FEJUSIBU BIHA MEN JESHA’U WE HUM JUXHADILUNE FI ELLAHI WE HUWE SHEDIDUL-MIHALI
  13,14,LEHU DA’WETUL-HEKKI WEL-LEDHINE JED’UNE MIN DUNIHI LA JESTEXHIBUNE LEHUM BISHEJ’IN ‘ILLA KEBASITI KEFFEJHI ‘ILAL-MA’I LIJEBLUGA FAHU WE MA HUWE BIBALIGIHI WE MA DU’A’UL-KAFIRINE ‘ILLA FI DELALIN
  13,15,WE LILLEHI JESXHUDU MEN FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI TEW’ÆN WE KERHÆN WE DHILALUHUM BIL-GUDUWI WEL-’ASALI
  13,16,KUL MEN REBBU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI KULI ELLAHU KUL ‘EFATTEHADHTUM MIN DUNIHI ‘EWLIJA’E LA JEMLIKUNE LI’NFUSIHIM NEF’ÆN WE LA DERRÆN KUL HEL JESTEWIL-’A’MA WEL-BESIRU ‘EM HEL TESTEWI EDH-DHULUMATU WE EN-NUR ‘EM XHE’ALU LILLAHI SHUREKA’E HALEKU KEHALKIHI F
  13,17,‘ENZELE MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN FESALET ‘EWDIJETUN BIKADERIHA FAHTEMELE ES-SEJLU ZEBEDÆN RABIÆN WE MIMMA JUKIDUNE ‘ALEJHI FI EN-NARI EBTIGA’E HILJETIN ‘EW META’IN ZEBEDUN MITHLUHU KEDHALIKE JEDRIBU ELLAHUL-HEKKA WEL-BATILE FE’EMMA EZ-ZEBEDU FEJEDH/HEBU XHUFA
  13,18,LILLEDHINE ESTEXHABU LIREBBIHIMUL-HUSNA WEL-LEDHINE LEM JESTEXHIBU LEHU LEW ‘ENNE LEHUM MA FIL-’ERDI XHEMI’ÆN WE MITHLEHU ME’AHU LAFTEDEW BIHI ‘ULA’IKE LEHUM SU’UL-HISABI WE ME’WAHUM XHEHENNEMU WE BI’SEL-MIHADU